comments: Zubac (LAC) jumps forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Haliburton's (IND) slightly extended off-arm during the driving shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) brushes Leonard's (LAC) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Leonard comes to a stop in the lane.
Hield (IND) turns slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Leonard's (LAC) front as Leonard passes.
Nesmith (IND) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) crosses half-court within eight seconds.
Zubac (LAC) legally contests Turner's (IND) jump shot attempt and would avoid Turner if he did not slightly extend his right leg forward to initiate the marginal contact.
Correctly called 24 second violation on Indiana.
Nembhard (IND) comes to a stop alongside Leonard (LAC) and absorbs the marginal body contact as Leonard leans toward him after receiving the pass.
Nembhard (IND) moves forward slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Leonard (LAC) at the end of Leonard's drive.
Turner's (IND) arms come forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Zubac's (LAC) left arm after Zubac takes his left hand away from the ball during his upward shooting motion.
Jackson (LAC) brings his right hand toward Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs with Haliburton's front as he drives inside the lane.
Turner (IND) and Zubac (LAC) engage with one another in the lane and marginal contact occurs before they disengage.
Jackson (LAC) extends forward and initiates body contact with Haliburton (IND) that alters his shot attempt in the lane.
Nembhard (IND) and Turner (IND) each jump forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Leonard's (LAC) left side as Leonard cuts back into the lane at the end of the drive.
Jackson (LAC) and Nembhard (IND) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.

Replay review of the foul called on George (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. George turns with his right arm extended forward and he initiates contact with Haliburton's (IND) front/side that affects his driving shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) engages and disengages with Kennard (LAC) off-ball.
Nesmith (IND) extends his left hand into George's (LAC) path and initiates contact with George's front during the drive.
Jackson (LAC) and Nembhard (IND) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Morris Sr. (LAC) commits a take foul on Turner (IND).
Turner (IND) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Morris Sr. (LAC) commits a take foul on Haliburton (IND).
Turner (IND) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
